'''Sullustan wine''' was an [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] beverage. It was a [[claret]].

[[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] planned to serve this beverage on the night that he almost proposed to [[Tonnika sisters/Legends|Bresenni]].

The liquid was also the preferred drink of [[Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina/Legends|Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina]] regulars the [[Tonnika sisters/Legends|Tonnika sisters]].

